# onto runtime data — per-session / ephemeral artifacts only.
# Structural resources migrated under `.onto/` by the repo-layout migration
# (Phase 1~6: commands/, domains/, roles/, processes/, principles/, authority/)
# are versioned and intentionally NOT ignored. If a new runtime-ephemeral
# subdirectory is added under `.onto/`, add its pattern here explicitly.
# CI guard: scripts/check-onto-allowlist.sh fails when a tracked `.onto/` path
# is neither in its structural allowlist nor covered by this file.
#
# Dogfooding exception: `.onto/config.yml` is *tracked* in this repo as a
# canonical reference for other onto-X consumers (dogfooding self-consistency,
# 2026-04-22). It is registered in the allowlist script's exact-match list.
# Other onto-X repos that consume this package can keep their own
# `.onto/config.yml` ignored locally — this exception is repo-scoped.
.onto/review/
.onto/builds/
.onto/learnings/
.onto/govern/
.onto/reconstruct/
.onto/temp/
.onto-review/
.claude/

# evolve scope artifacts (ephemeral design sessions)
scopes/
.sprint-kit/cache/
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
node_modules/

# dist/ is tracked as a transition bridge (A1 in activation-determinism
# redesign, 2026-04-23). Claude Code plugin install runs npm install with
# --ignore-scripts, so the `prepare` hook that would build dist/ is skipped.
# Committing dist/ gives plugin consumers a usable install from git clone.
# Sunset conditions (development-records/evolve/20260423-activation-determinism-
# redesign.md §3.1): (a) direct dist refs removed, (b) packaged execution
# topology drops dist dep, (c) activation_descriptor valid on fresh install,
# (d) package.json:files ships src or src+loader contract declared.
# drafts/ contains WIP design iterations (Activation Determinism Redesign
# v1~v6 v4 series). Kept local; not source of truth.
drafts/
